    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver despite showing signs of its age. The engine and transmission are functional, though you should expect some minor cosmetic wear such as small scratches on the exterior and some fading on the interior upholstery. It has been maintained regularly to keep it roadworthy, making it a practical choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly, functional car without the premium price of a newer model.",
